Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, what's the big hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's wrong? \N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys are probably Asakura scouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They came from the direction \Nof Daigo's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-I see. \N-Wait, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a really bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is in Daigo's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:27.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…もう少しゆっくり歩いてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:42.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:45.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうした\Nな…なんでもないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:46.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:50.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どけどけーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:03.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いまのやつら、たぶん朝倉の斥候だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.81,0:01:06.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それが醍醐領のほうから走ってきた！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:09.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか…\N待ってくれあにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.19,0:01:12.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら…なんだか嫌な予感がするよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:14.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,構わない。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐に身体がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed this world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And it simmers within
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupturing my innards
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.96,0:02:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Swelling a reddish black
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.09,0:02:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the sun burnt skin ruptures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the seething darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,#21 The story of breaking the cycle of suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Two new villages in the territory \Nhave been affected by the epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn down the villages. \NMake sure it doesn't spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The Asakura clan is gathering up \Ntheir army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Around 2,000 soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are they about to advance? \N-No sir, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How about our army and its provisions?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:04:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We're rounding up men from allies \Nand unaffected villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The days of prosperity \Nfor this land are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All men who can walk \Nwill be drafted as soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you pardon just a couple of men?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The women and children \Ncan't handle all the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This land is in danger. \NWhat is more important!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined you'd come this far \Nto round up horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be quite a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fine horse. We'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Midoro is my finest horse. \NShe's our breadwinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return her to us unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for that. \NWe are fighting for our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You will obey me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You, lend a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're positive it's Hyakkimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am quite sure. \NThat child is also with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He will reach this territory \Nwithin a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So he has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Asakura will be on the move by then. \NWhat shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall go and dispose of Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A small troop would be no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, we cannot afford to send \Na whole army just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I will need no other \Nas long as I have Mutsu and Hyogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, if we don't dispose \Nof Hyakkimaru now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we will never be able to \Ngovern this land in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. Go, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When we reach Daigo, what if, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do \Nif your papa and mama come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If they get in my way, I will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll never ever be able \Nto be by their side again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Will many die again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how we almost did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We must defeat Hyakkimaru \Nand bring an end to all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let my people \Nsuffer any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us go exorcise the evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So Tahomaru has gone for Hyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru is like a baby \Nwho has come crying to take his toy back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No words can reach him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is the same for Tahomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He is turning himself into an incarnation \Nof Asura for the sake of Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The wife of a lord, \Nor the mother of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Had I have been just one and not both, \NI wouldn't have cursed my helplessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you two from Daigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you better turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gonna be a huge war here \Nwith Asakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I came all this way because \Nthey said I'd make a fortune here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But hey, nothing's more precious \Nthan your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard him, there's going to be a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel, \Nbut now isn't the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm getting my body back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you heard the old guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's more precious \Nthan your life, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. But I'm not going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? They're the ones that took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to become someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I not be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To touch with my hands. \NTo see with my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh dang it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I just seem to be a bit tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is just like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been together for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How long has it been \Nsince Lord Daigo saved Hyogo and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have done well to survive. \NDon't worry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you sharpened a corpse's bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest easy, I am not your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mutsu and Hyogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They will stay here from today on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They will study and train with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsu, Hyogo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will strive for peace \Ntogether with my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So no more people die senseless deaths \Nor go through such hardships as you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that, I will make Daigo \Nthe strongest domain in the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Our aspirations are as one \Nwith yours and Lord Daigo's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have humbly become your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo has become your left. \NWe will protect you with all that we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the day \Nyour ambitions are fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The day is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not let this domain fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Onward, march!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance! Daigo is nothing to be afraid of!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, it's them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't! He's your little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He called me a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,His rage is unlike before. \NBe careful, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:17:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru. \NYou will not harm this land any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Tahomaru, will slay you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,His right arm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You demon, bane of our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill you \Nif it's the last thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, bro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Daigo ordered me \Nto look after you discreetly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahomaru will succeed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure he returns to this castle alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you must retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I must defeat Hyakkimaru \Nor this land will be done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-They are the lord's orders. \N-I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakki... maru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it. Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I said let go of me, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyakkimaru is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We need him, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It is cowardly to use the helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I care not for your sentiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it breaks you, \Neven if it turns you into the devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your job to protect Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shame on you for being saved by him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do... roro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:27.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,申し上げます！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:32.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,新たに領内2つの村で、流行り病いが出た模様でございます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:33.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やむを得まい。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:39.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,村ごと焼き払え。近隣まで広がらぬようにいたせ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:41.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,申し上げます！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:45.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,朝倉軍、着々と兵が集まりつつあるとのこと！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その数、およそ2千！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:52.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,動きそうか\Nいえ…まだその気配は見られませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が軍の兵と兵糧はどうなっている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:04:00.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,同盟国、および災難に見舞われていない村からの徴用確保を\N進めておりますが…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:02.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今だ充分とは…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,遅い！急がせろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:14.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この国の安寧のときは…終わりまする
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:25.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,嫌だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:30.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,許せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:36.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,動ける男は残れ！兵として徴用する！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:38.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,モタモタするな！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:42.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,せめて2、3人だけ村に残すわけにはいかねぇですか。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:45.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,女子供だけじゃぁ、力仕事が…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:48.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,国の一大事に、気にかけている場合か！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:56.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こんな辺鄙なところまで馬を取りにおいでなさるとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よほどのことなんで？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:04.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おぉ…これは見事な馬だ！貰うぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:08.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このミドロは、うちの稼ぎ頭でして
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうか怪我をさせずに戻してくださいまし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:15.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,勝手なことを言うな！我らは国のために戦うのだぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:19.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,さぁ来い…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,言うことを聞け！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.11,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,な…なんてことを…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:35.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前も手を貸せぃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:49.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,着々とこちらへと向かっております
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:52.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,間違いなく百鬼丸だろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:57.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,確かにございます。いつも連れている子供もおりました。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:00.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,数日のうちに領内へ入るかと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やはり来るか…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.94,0:06:07.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その頃には朝倉も動くはず。いかがいたしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:11.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならば私が百鬼丸を討ちます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:19.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵をいくらか集めたとて、奴にはかないませぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:24.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,とはいえ今は、全軍を向かわせるわけにもいきますまい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:30.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥と兵庫がいれば、他に兵は要りません。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:37.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,父上。ここで百鬼丸を討てぬならば、
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:41.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この先醍醐を治めていくことなど到底できませぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:45.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よかろう。行ってまいれ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よろしいので？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あの目を見たであろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,止められはせぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,…お前にやってもらうことがある
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぁ。あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:17.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:22.44,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐に行ってさ。もしも…もしもまた、
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:26.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきのお父ちゃんやおっかちゃんが来たら…どうするんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:29.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,邪魔するなら…斬る
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:34.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも、そんなことしたらこの先一生…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何があっても、そばにいられなくなっちまうんだぞ！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:41.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろがいる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:04.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何をしている。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:06.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若がお待ちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,また…たくさん死ぬのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:13.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのときの俺らのような人たちが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戦は嫌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:52.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ。何としても百鬼丸を倒し、終わらせなければならぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わかっている…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:56.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これ以上…この国の民を苦しませるわけにはいかぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,災いを払いに行くぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.27,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうでしたか…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:08.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸は、百鬼丸の元へ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:09.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:21.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今の百鬼丸は…\N取り上げられた玩具を泣いて取り戻しに来る幼子のようなもの。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:26.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,きっと…誰の言葉も届かないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そしてそれは…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:35.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐のため、修羅の化身となろうとする多宝丸も同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:40.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,領主の妻か、子を持つ母か。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:46.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どちらか一方であったなら、己の無力さを呪うこともなかったでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,御方様…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:51.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:53.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…おい、ちょっと待ちな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたら、醍醐の人かい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:09.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,違うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:13.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,だったら悪いことは言わねぇ。すぐに引き返せ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:15.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうすぐ朝倉との大いくさが始まるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:22.64,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ったく醍醐に行きゃ儲けられるって言うから、\Nこの田舎くんだりまで来たのによぉ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんたらも、命あっての物種だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あぁ…おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:37.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:40.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,邪魔…するな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何やってんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.83,0:11:54.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき、聞いたろ！？やっぱり戦が起こるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,気持ちはわかるけど、今はやめよう！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:12:00.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメだ。身体を取り戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.97,0:12:02.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今はおっちゃんの言うとおりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,死んじまったらどうにもなんないんだってば！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,取り戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,うっ！だったらおいら、ついて行ってやんねーぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:21.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜだ。奪ったのは奴らだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらはただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきがあにきでなくなっちまうのが嫌なんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:27.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,怖いんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:30.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ俺じゃなくなる！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:36.67,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺の手で触る\N俺の目で見る！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺も感じる…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:41.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろと同じに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:50.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちくしょう…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:55.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら…どうしたらいいんだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:01.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちくしょう…ちくしょう…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:17.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:20.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,えぇ。どうやら少し気が張っているようで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そうか…珍しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.38,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:28.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,相変わらずか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,困ったものです
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:35.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,思えばずいぶんと共にいるな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:38.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,景光様に助けられ、もう何年になりますか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,よくぞ生き抜いた。もう大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:10.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,骸の骨を削ったか。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:12.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,案ずるな。我らは敵ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:18.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.52,0:14:21.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここにおるは陸奥と兵庫だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:23.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今日よりこの屋敷にとどめ置く。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.94,0:14:28.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これからは共に学問や剣術に励め
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥。兵庫。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:40.92,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私は父上とともに、太平の世を目指す。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:47.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こうして死にゆく者も、お前たちのように辛い思いをする者もいない世だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:56.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのために…醍醐を天下一の強国にするぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.52,0:15:04.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我らが望みは、景光様と若の宿願に同じ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:08.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,私は及ばずながら、若の右腕となり、
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:13.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫は左腕として宿願成就のその時まで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:15.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,全身全霊でお守りいたします
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,成就の時は…すぐそこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:22.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:32.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この国を…終わらせはせぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.76,0:15:35.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いざ！出陣！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:50.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,進めぇー！醍醐など恐るるに足らずー！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:28.52,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき、またあいつらが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:31.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.49,0:16:33.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,離れていろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:37.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ダメだあにき！あいつはあにきの弟だぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,違う！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:42.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれは…俺を鬼神と呼んだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:53.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,前とは比べ物にならぬ殺気。ご用心を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:17:00.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸…これ以上醍醐を穢させはせん。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:03.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この多宝丸が、ここで貴様を討つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,陸奥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:22.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:35.05,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,右腕が！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐に仇なす鬼神め…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:41.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この命を懸けて、貴様を葬ってくれる！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:32.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ぁあにき…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:40.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前はこっちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:42.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,離せ！うっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:46.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！あにきぃーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ貴様が…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:54.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,景光様の命により、密かにお守りしておりました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:58.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多宝丸は醍醐の世継ぎ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.32,0:20:02.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,必ず生きてこの城に戻らせよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:05.87,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここは退いてくださいませ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:10.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸を倒さねば、この国は滅ぶ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:15.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,殿の命にございます！\N聞かぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:18.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,御免…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:27.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼…丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:31.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お運びしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:38.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！やめろよ…離せよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:41.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！離せってんだバカヤロ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:43.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その子供は！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:45.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸にとどめを刺せておらぬ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,万が一のためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,力なき者を利用するは卑劣！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:53.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様らの理屈などどうでもよい！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:57.59,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,己の身が滅びようが、その魂を捻じ曲げようが、
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若をお守りするのがお役目であろう！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:02.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ貴様らが若に助けられている！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:15.69,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行くぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…あにきぃーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:46.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…ど…ろろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.28,0:22:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The distorted shape of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:23:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it beats courageously
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the withering seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We search for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.22,0:23:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even recognize the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As we peel back the skin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.78,0:23:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever tormented by our stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the dawn never comes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.91,0:23:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the painful night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.04,0:23:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You who distrusts nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.17,0:23:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to love  \N this accursed world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.21,0:23:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we carry the world  \N on our shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.63,0:23:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.05,0:23:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"Midoro"
